		<div id="comment_body_64624713">Every decade and a half I switch jobs radically. Skilled technician is next on my list. Don't need to be able to do planning, if the orders get low, just listen to your voice mail and pick someone you like. Do a mediocre job, be late on the appointment, charge through the roof and people are still glad you dropped by. I may buy a pickup truck.</div>
